154
00:10:03,919 --> 00:10:04,720
Lady Shen.

155
00:10:06,080 --> 00:10:06,879
I'm sorry.

156
00:10:09,279 --> 00:10:10,320
I'll leave now.

157
00:10:20,840 --> 00:10:22,039
Senior,

158
00:10:22,039 --> 00:10:23,000
