159
00:10:23,000 --> 00:10:23,840
Senior.

160
00:10:32,000 --> 00:10:33,240
Dear, take this.

161
00:10:33,240 --> 00:10:35,200
If you encounter great trouble one day,

162
00:10:35,200 --> 00:10:36,679
