214
00:12:46,120 --> 00:12:48,080
Please do not ask.

215
00:12:48,759 --> 00:12:49,279
Okay.

216
00:12:50,000 --> 00:12:51,279
I won't ask about this.

217
00:12:51,279 --> 00:12:53,440
