221
00:13:05,799 --> 00:13:06,960
I bought a bag for you.

222
00:13:13,559 --> 00:13:15,879
Tomorrow is a big day for you.

223
00:13:16,840 --> 00:13:18,080
So I'd like to

224
00:13:25,799 --> 00:13:26,600
