225
00:13:30,440 --> 00:13:32,440
No worry, I'm not controlled.

226
00:13:34,519 --> 00:13:35,136
Dear.

227
00:13:35,799 --> 00:13:38,879
Why are you suddenly like this?

228
00:13:40,759 --> 00:13:41,720
